1.演者の初期配置
2.演出開始

Queen Leucos: Rex... Listen carefully, there is something I
must apologize to you for.

Queen Leucos: I apologize for not being able to witness the
day you sit on the throne and for not being able to
participate in your wedding ceremony.
Queen Leucos: And...

Queen Leucos: I apologize for not being able to kill the
monster within you.

Queen Leucos: Even if I kept it hidden, I could sense the
same thing from Agnos-sama from time to time.

Queen Leucos: What is within you... is something much
greater than Agnos-sama.
Prince Rex: Mother, that is...!

Queen Leucos: It is our responsibility, the responsibility
of educating the king, the responsibility of placing you
between the education of the king and the education of the
believers...

Queen Leucos: Please seal away the monster within your heart
for the rest of your life. It is for your sake and for the
sake of the Fotizona Empire.

Queen Leucos: Sitting on the throne is the king, not a
dragon wearing a crown...

Queen Leucos had intended to give Rex advice with good
intentions. However, for Rex, it was a complete denial of
his personality.

I don't want you to acknowledge the monster within me.
However, that monster is a part of who I am as Rex. My
mother's advice completely shattered my confidence in
becoming a king.

After Queen Leucos died, her lover Caron and father Agnos
remarried. This became the final blow for Rex. He believed
that his role as a prince had been completely discarded.

Moreover, the second prince, Katala, was born. Rex decided
to completely abandon the idea of becoming king. It was
something that no one desired, and he himself had also
stopped desiring it.

However, Rex had not told anyone about it. His habit of not
expressing his thoughts would lead to the worst possible
situation.

With the death of King Agnos, Rex was captured by the
guards. Queen Caron had instigated a coup. Rex, who had lost
both his mother and father, was being crushed by guilt
inside the cage.

Everything was brought about by the monster within myself. I
continued to believe that as my mother said, the monster
should have died.

However, that very fact became food for the monster. And the
monster speaks to Rex's subconscious.

Break the cage, set yourself free, and then you can become
anything. A hero, a sage, and of course, even a king... You
can have it all, just as you wish.
イベント終了用
